      "rationale": "Numerical code verification performed via method of manufactured solutions (MMS) for the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver and the scalar transport equation used for hemolysis index advection. Observed order of convergence (OOC) for velocity: 1.97 (theoretical 2nd order); for pressure: 1.94; for hemolysis scalar: 1.96. All OOC values within 5% of theoretical. Verification suite documented in technical report TR-CV-2025-04 with full MMS source term derivations.",
